description:
NEW: Always wanted to walk into a bar and leave the next  iPhone 5 prototype on the table! Here you go!
******************************** Will YOU like it? Download for free and tell us what you think. ******************************** Best prank ever: start Prankster, put your Pre on a table and wait for your friends eventually picking up your phone. It will lite up magically and shows an iPhone look alike screen. Watch them while they launch an app...
*************************************
The pulsing screen is not an error, really.
